<div class="container-fluid text-center">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 mb-5 mt-5">
      <h1 class="display-3 lead">Welcome to Your Journey of Growth</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 text-md-start">
      <p class="lead fw-bolder">Inspire and be inspired! </p>
      <p class="lead fw-bolder">Welcome to our inclusive community where you can freely
        express yourself and connect with others on your journey of
        self-discovery and personal growth.
      </p>
      <p class="lead fw-bolder">Share your thoughts, experiences, and insights with
        others, and be inspired by the stories and wisdom of fellow members.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div id="imageCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img
              src="/images/miguel-bruna-TzVN0xQhWaQ-unsplash.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100"
              style="max-height: 500px;"
              alt="..."
            />
            <div class="carousel-text">Small steps lead to big changes. Keep
              moving forward.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="/images/birgith-roosipuu--zLsm1cV2Ss-unsplash.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100"
              style="max-height: 500px;"
              alt="..."
            />
            <div class="carousel-text">Success is not final, failure is not
              fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="/images/tim-goedhart-vnpTRdmtQ30-unsplash.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100"
              style="max-height: 500px;"
              alt="..."
            />
            <div class="carousel-text">You are the author of your own story.
              Write it with courage, resilience, and determination.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img
              src="/images/christina-deravedisian-VDOhTPhJZb0-unsplash.jpg"
              class="d-block w-100"
              style="max-height: 500px;"
              alt="..."
            />
            <div class="carousel-text">Believe in your potential, for you are
              capable of achieving greatness.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button
          class="carousel-control-prev"
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#imageCarousel"
          data-bs-slide="prev"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button
          class="carousel-control-next"
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#imageCarousel"
          data-bs-slide="next"
        >
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="arrow-container">
  <div class="arrow"></div>
</div>

